summary: Adds a basic Farmhouse style home in Riverwood across from the Inn. Good home in a small town. The home does have some hidden secrets though.
descriptionHtml:
[color=#ff0000][size=5]Not updating this mod as i am no longer modding (much better modders out there). If you want to modify or redo this please be my guest![/size][/color]



I made this for myself and thought that I would share it.

Adds a basic Farmhouse style home in Riverwood across from the Inn.

Features:
Chopping Block
Sharpening Wheel
Workbench
Alchemy Table
Enchanting Table
Anvil
Hidden Armory with plenty of storage and Displays (has cavern exit for those times of quick escape).
Complete Navmesh
Plenty of Chests and Bookshelves

I am still very new to Modding so let me know what you think and endorse if you like.
author: Guitarman007
